"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: non=
e !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; borde=
r-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">but be careful</a>:</p><blo=
ckquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A few weeks before Digital World Acqui=
sition announced a deal to merge with a fledgling social media company back=
ed by former President Donald J. Trump, it was at the center of a sudden tr=
ading frenzy. ...</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">About 350,000 warrants of=
 Digital World traded in the first two days. But on the third day =E2=80=94=
 Oct. 4, a week after Digital World and Trump Media &amp; Technology Group =
entered into formal talks that were not disclosed at the time =E2=80=94 tra=
ding in the warrants exploded. More than 2.5 million changed hands that day=
.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The surge was unusual, especially f=
