</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Someone sold a Bored Ape Yacht Club no=
n-fungible token for <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cli=
ck/26026573.275653/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY25ldC5jb20vZ29vZ2xlLWFtcC9uZXdzL2JvcmVk=
