rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Miner Extractable Value<=
/a>=E2=80=9D in the literature, people <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/26026573.275653/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXNlYXJjaC5wYXJhZGlnbS54eX=
ovTUVW/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBca9bf172" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
