to the Michael Lewis book about traditional equity market structure) =E2=80=
=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26026573.275653=
/aHR0cHM6Ly9hcnhpdi5vcmcvYWJzLzE5MDQuMDUyMzQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB6bb6d=
bc5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=
